						<summary>

						<p>Slab set up in the Chennakēśava temple.</p>						

						<p>Sadāśiva, 1546 A.D.</p>						

						<p>This is dated <hi rend="bold">Śaka 1468, Parābhava, Kārttika śu. 12</hi> corresponding to <hi rend="bold">1546 A.D. November 5, Friday °22.</hi></p>						

						<p>Seems to record a gift of umbrella to the god Vēṅkaṭēśvara at Peda yakalūru in Jagatāpi-Gutti-<hi rend="italic">sīma</hi> by Śrī <hi rend="italic">Mahāmaṇḍalēśvara</hi> Rāmarāju, son of Śriṅgāyadēva mahārāju.</p>						

						</summary>
